{"tid":1115304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遊日注意】東京鬧市有一萬隻蜜蜂亂飛 疑尋覓新巢致集體飛行","createTime":"2019-04-19T05:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T07:04:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13e1b0a89f959482da416309b2d06ecd89a4a12f","tid":1115304,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"日本東京澀谷區昨早有上萬隻蜜蜂在街頭亂飛，不少途人緊張走避，當局要請來養蜂人處理。<br />\n事發在昨早9時左右，澀谷區惠比壽一丁目有約1萬隻蜜蜂亂飛，每隻體長約1厘米。其中一名60多歲途人表示很怕被螫到，跑着離開現場。<br />\n區公所稱接到約10宗蜜蜂亂飛的報告，雖然無人受傷，但由於附近有小學，已派職員查看，並請來養蜂人長島房子放置蜂巢箱，希望把蜜蜂收走。<br />\n長島房子表示目前正是蜜蜂群中新蜂后誕生的時期，原本的蜂后為了尋覓新蜂巢，便帶同其他蜂群集體飛行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190419/large/1555651568_e66f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190419%2Flarge%2F1555651568_e66f.jpg&h=0f93a3e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190419/large/1555638189_7809.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190419%2Flarge%2F1555638189_7809.jpg&h=28aa3fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190419/large/1555635862_3e0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190419%2Flarge%2F1555635862_3e0d.jpg&h=49d01898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190419/59505951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190419%2F59505951&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0078b995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190419%2F59505951&h=b3c496a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190419/59505951</a>"},{"pid":"09a9ba98cd2d1202d6f7cb25700310ebfbc20898","tid":1115304,"uid":89530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:46:37.000Z","msg":"希望可以安全搵到新屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蜜蜂益蟲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4b2aad7cd1d0e8028a1a8d4844d03696da8dc1","tid":1115304,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"我以前屋企都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49dbb980bb2b8eb6656ee31b2d94bcf10da122c","tid":1115304,"uid":1067,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"屌！用津路水炮啦"},{"pid":"1a44a7cfb54921c17b6c06dbe2a22d4a325bd506","tid":1115304,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}